      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_49059220-1EEE-0135-EDE7-22000BC102FE" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Hover over the timestamp of the message you want to delete to view more options. Select the <strong>Delete</strong> link.</p>
<p><strong>Note</strong>: You can only select one message to delete at a time.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="confirm_deletion" data-step-uuid="7416f612-c3b2-47b3-b626-5cf7ac633f0a">
