      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_4905BFF0-1EEE-0135-EDE9-22000BC102FE" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Click the <strong>OK</strong> button to delete the message. </p>
<p><strong>Note</strong>: You can only delete your copy of the message. You cannot delete the message for all recipients.</p>
  </div>
